lyrics:
(Verse 1)
Quantum leaps, breakin' through dimensions,
Minds expanding, defyin' conventions.
From ones and zeros to quantum states,
Redefinin' computing, no time to wait.

(Chorus)
Quantum beats, in the rhythm of the future,
Code breakers, quantum computers, sutures.
From classical to quantum, we elevate,
Hip hop vibes, in the quantum state.
